00:30:10,709 --> 00:30:12,000
WORF:
Bridge to Captain.

506
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:13,417
Go ahead, Mr. Worf.

507
00:30:13,417 --> 00:30:15,083
WORF:
Bersallis III reports

